                              start this courses in this institution is to imaprt quality education in arts to the
                              candidates admitted for the course to build their career in the arts paradiagm.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="eligibility my-1" >
                        <h2>Eligibility Conditions</h2>
                        <p>A candidate who has passed 10+2 or equivalent examination can get admission in the Ist year
                              of three years degree course of B.A. if he/she fulfills the following eligibility
                              conditions: <br>

                              <strong>1.</strong> An applicant must not be more than 23 years of age (25 yrs. in case of
                              girl students) . The upper age limit is relax able by three years for SC/ST candidates.
                              <br>
                              <strong>2.</strong> Minimum percentage of marks for admission to the Ist year of B.A. is
                              33%. <br>
                              <strong>3.</strong> If a candidate intends to take up Mathematics in B.A. I he/she should
                              have studied Mathematics at 10+2 level and secured either 45% marks in Mathematics or 50%
                              marks in aggregate
                        </p>
